definition.value: Heterogeneous cluster which consists of two or more adjacent bones or cartilages, parts of  which are interconnected by organ parts that consist of various types of connective tissue. Together with other joints and bones, a joint constitutes the skeletal system. Examples: pubic symphysis, knee joint, temporomandibular joint.
